Roger Davis (film actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Roger_Davis_(film_actor) 0 Roger Davis (born April 5, 1939) is an American actor and entrepreneur. He is best known for acting in television series Dark Shadows and Alias Smith and Jones. He also appeared on an episode of The Twilight Zone.
